column2: SELECT u.up_name as name,     &&& + cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec,     dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,    p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,s.z as redshift, pmodelMag_z FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID        LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll s p.ObjID = s.bestObjID where p.type = # ORDER  BY x.up_id
